Blog posts: 50~5,000 CGT depending on the quality of the article  YouTube videos: 100~200k CGT depending on the quality of the video  Translation: 4,000 CGT for translating our whitepaper  *Please note the dollar values were calculated when the whitepaper was written and may vary depending on the market price of ETH. *each participant can make maximum of 1 ETH worth of CGTs (1 ETH = 500 CGTs) from social bounties (Twitter and Facebook combined)    Public ICO 23rd November 2018 ~ 23rd June 2019  [Whitelist now!] https://www.coingrid.co.nz/kyc    Official website: www.coingrid.co.nz Whitepaper: https://www.coingrid.co.nz/whitepaper.pdf Prototype/MVP: https://prototype.coingrid.co.nz Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/coingridnz/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/CoingridNZ Telegram: https://t.me/coingridnz Discord: https://discord.gg/hpxVpJT      Bounty signup HERE: https://www.coingrid.co.nz/bounty      UP TO 2 MILLION TOKENS TO GIVE AWAY! Our bounty campaign will commence on 25 June 2018 and will continue through until the end of the ICO process. The ICO process will end on 23 June 2019 or when the hard cap is reached.  Token Price 1 ETH = 500 CGT      Tokens will be distributed within 2 weeks from the date ICO ends.  PLEASE POST A REPORT ON THIS THREAD WHEN YOU COMPLETE THE BOUNTY *Please note that you do not have to follow a specific format for the "Proof Comments" but you will need to follow the rules.  Example:  Proof Of Participation: Twitter link: https://twitter.com/Crxw3ll Posts liked & shared on Twitter: https://twitter.com/CoingridNZ/status/1060004484376551424 https://twitter.com/CoingridNZ/status/1057215768339705856 https://twitter.com/CoingridNZ/status/1056473496988016640 https://twitter.com/CoingridNZ/status/1046531781812342785 Telegram username: @ceocoingrid     Telegram Bounty  Join our Telegram chat and earn 2.5 CGT !  Bounty Rules  1. You must join our official Telegram channel at https://t.me/coingridnz 2. You must stay in our official channel until the end of ICO. Accounts that have left the chatroom early will not receive their reward. 3. Bots are not allowed and participating accounts must be genuine. 4. Spamming, trolling, advertising and/or other actions that are not appropriate to the community will not be tolerated. 5. Any users who fail to follow the rules will be disqualified.    How to Participate  1. Join our Telegram chat at https://t.me/coingridnz 2. Make sure you specify your Telegram handle on your bounty form at http://www.coingrid.co.nz/bounty   Discord Bounty  Join our Discord chat and earn 2.5 CGT !  Bounty Rules  1. How to Participate  1. Join our Discord chat at https://discordapp.com/invite/rppPd8q 2. Make sure you specify your Telegram handle on your bounty form at http://www.coingrid.co.nz/bounty   Twitter Bounty  Follow our Twitter page and earn 2.5 CGT 1 like on our post will reward you 1 CGT 1 retweeting of our post will reward you 1 CGT Tweet about Coingrid for 5 CGT a post *this can only be done once a day and must contain #ico #bitcoin #ethereum #cryptocurrency and #coingrid This can be done as much as you want.  EG: Like and retweet 10 posts for 20 CGTs !  Bounty Rules  1. Your account must have over 50 Followers 2. Must follow our official Twitter at https://twitter.com/CoingridNZ 3. You must like at least 5 Tweets posted by @CoingridNZ 4. You must retweet at least 5 Tweets posted by @CoingridNZ 5. Your followers must be genuine, any users who used bots and/or boosters to gain fake followers will be disqualified. 6. Only real accounts can participate (no bots) 7. Please provide links to the posts that you liked/retweeted on this thread for accurate calculations   How to Participate  1. Follow, like and retweet accordingly at https://twitter.com/CoingridNZ 2. Make sure you provide your Twitter details on your bounty form at http://www.coingrid.co.nz/bounty 3. Report to this thread once you have completed your task (refer to example at the top/bottom of the post)  Facebook Bounty  Follow our Facebook page and earn 3 CGT 1 like on our post will reward you 1 CGT 1 share of our post will reward you 2 CGT This can be done as much as you want.  EG: Like and share 10 posts for 30 CGTs!  Bounty Rules  1. Your account must have over 100 Friends 2. Must follow our official Facebook Page at https://www.facebook.com/coingridnz/ 3. You must like at least 5 posts posted by @CoingridNZ 4. You must share at least 5 posts posted by @CoingridNZ 5. Your friends must be genuine, any users who used bots and/or boosters to gain fake friends will be disqualified. 6. Only real accounts can participate (no bots) 7. Your Facebook account must allow â€œPublicâ€ to view your Friends list 8. Please provide links to the posts that you liked/shared   How to Participate  1. Follow, like and share accordingly at https://www.facebook.com/coingridnz/ 2. Make sure you specify your Facebook details on your bounty form at http://www.coingrid.co.nz/bounty 3. Report to this thread once you have completed your task (refer to example at the top/bottom of the post)   Blogs and Articles Bounty  50~5,000 CGT depending on the quality of the article Please send us a draft and link to your blog for quotation  Bounty Rules  1. Your blog or platform or website must have an audience (at least 15 likes on Steemit, or 15 claps on Medium) 2. The article must be at least 300 words long 3. Article must describe at least two of our key features. 4. Article must contain the link to our website www.coingrid.co.nz 5. Content must be in English, Korean, Japanese or Russian.    How to Participate  1. Write/post your article. 2. Make sure you specify the link to your article on your bounty form at http://www.coingrid.co.nz/bounty 3.
